\sum_{k=0}^{n}k^22^{n-k}
2^{n-k}=\sum_{j=0}^{n-k}\binom{n-k}{j}
\sum_{k=0}^{n}k^22^{n-k}=\sum_{k=0}^{n}k^2\sum_{j=0}^{n-k}\binom{n-k}{j}
-n^2-4n+6(2^n-1)
A(z) = \sum_k a_k z^k
 \sum_{0 \le k \le n} z^k = \frac{z^{n + 1} - 1}{z - 1} 
 z \frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d} z} A(z) = \sum_k k a_k z^k 
\sum_{k=0}^nk^22^{n-k}=2^n\sum_{k=0}^nk^2\left(\frac12\right)^k
\displaystyle S=\sum_{k=0}^nk^2r^k
\displaystyle\implies r\cdot S=\sum_{k=0}^nk^2r^{k+1}
\displaystyle\implies S-r\cdot S=\sum_{k=1}^n[k^2-(k-1)^2]r^{k+1}-n^2r^{n+1}
\displaystyle S(1-r)=-n^2r^{n+1}+\sum_{k=1}^n(2k-1)r^{k+1}
